headline: Why Viatris (VTRS) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of medication company Viatris (NASDAQ:VTRS) jumped 6.4% in the afternoon session after investment bank UBS upgraded the company's stock from "Neutral" to "Buy" and increased its price target.
